{"tid":1521805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紋身都整得甩，顏色水實有方法嘅","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:24:51.000Z","uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48627bc23edf9df82df3be758159a28f6624880e","tid":1521805,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"但要化學專家先識呢啲嘢"},{"pid":"9f2f99d5961a1cfbe57df7ce3aa74848bc047d58","tid":1521805,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"酒精抹手紙"},{"pid":"a83577cbf7e38d76e9dff209cfd6cea7cef76635","tid":1521805,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"afc677d61100b8610c84931f2024303b73fff3d9","tid":1521805,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"[quote]酒精抹手紙"},{"pid":"219809d1b7e841f7da56db8f922c0cbc108fa3a0","tid":1521805,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f2f99d5961a1cfbe57df7ce3aa74848bc047d58","tid":1521805,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"酒精抹手紙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"未乾就用得酒精<br />\nAcrylic 乾左就變一層膜, 唔溶水 唔溶酒精 唔溶天拿水<br />\n只能刮甩、磨走、大力卒甩<br />\n<br />\n利申：模型撚"},{"pid":"2af0322de52443d088407df22e67a69abbb4ea80","tid":1521805,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"大家！應該可以試下用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">番梘</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗走d染料，個source來自wiki當年purple Rain Protest<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbSKaXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbSKaXx.jpg&h=29f396ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請幫手試，如果ok請spread開去，p牌仔推唔到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望幫到人<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Purple_Rain_protest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPurple_Rain_protest&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4Wr6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=a99575dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Purple_Rain_protest</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SysNS8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSysNS8v.jpg&h=49aa8a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢第2個方法係用<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>1比100 HCL:水</strong></span></ins>洗，大家試左梘先應該work"}]}